value: It's hot, and they are craving water!\nTime to dig beneath the dry sand...
Oh no! It's not water; it's a scorpion!\nOnly their sweat saturates the sand...
A small puddle of water surfaces.\nFinally, they quench their thirst. Ah...
Surprisingly, a desert oasis appears!\nTheir bodies and spirits are refreshed.
$aFoes grant 5x SP for the next $a0,\nand then 2x SP thereafter! (Only highest\nvalue applied. Does not stack.)
